"{\"uid\": \"eppingforestguardian.co.uk-news-national-24272215.police-clear-migrant-camp-central-paris-pre-olympics-sweep-say-aid-groups\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  French police have evicted migrants from a makeshift camp in Paris a few steps from the River Seine in the latest operation in what aid groups call a campaign of \\\"social cleansing\\\" ahead of the Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.533522206410113e-33, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 63, \"end\": 68, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 30 teenage boys and young men from West Africa were woken before dawn by officers and urged to pack their tents and belongings.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 256, \"end\": 267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999803930385015, \"rank\": 1.9607254263223185e-05, \"text\": \"West Africa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/West_Africa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of them were underage and in the process of seeking residency papers.\", \"from\": 349, \"to\": 423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was already scared but I am even more scared because I do not know where to go,\\\" 16-year-old Boubacar Traore - who said he had fled conflict in Burkina Faso and arrived in France two months ago - said.\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 521, \"end\": 536, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boubacar_Traor\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.9999999946730895, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boubacar Traore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boubacar_Traor\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boubacar_Traor\\u00e9\"}, {\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\", \"score\": 0.9999999977101197, \"rank\": 2.289877893595625e-09, \"text\": \"Burkina Faso\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Burkina_Faso\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995463190012037, \"rank\": 0.0003072203020432395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The operation came days after police carried out a large-scale eviction at France's biggest squatter camp in a suburb south of Paris.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9995463190012037, \"rank\": 0.0003072203020432395, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 758, \"end\": 763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Such evictions and evacuations of migrant tent camps happen every spring after the end of a winter \\\"truce\\\" during which authorities put such actions on hold.\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 923, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But aid groups working with migrants and other vulnerable people in the Paris region said these efforts were intensifying ahead of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1069, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 997, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They noted that people were being sent far away from the capital instead of being offered shelter in the Paris region, where many asylum seekers have upcoming court dates.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The authorities want to have a clean place for the Olympics Games.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not want the tourists to see Paris as a city full of migrants and asylum seekers,\\\" Elias Hufnagel, a volunteer with a group serving refugees and immigrants, said at the Paris tent camp on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"score\": 0.9998827363239403, \"rank\": 0.00011727742864972986, \"text\": \"Elias\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elijah\"}, {\"begin\": 1409, \"end\": 1417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Siegfried_Hufnagel\", \"score\": 0.99999999583315, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hufnagel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Siegfried_Hufnagel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Siegfried_Hufnagel\"}, {\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris police said the operation was carried out for security reasons, notably because the tent camp was near schools.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two large buses heading to Besancon, 240 miles (400km) southeast of Paris, were stood in a nearby street.\", \"from\": 1637, \"to\": 1742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1664, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Besan\\u00e7on\", \"score\": 0.9995509536969429, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Besancon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Besan\\u00e7on\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Besan\\u00e7on\"}, {\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999991632194, \"rank\": 8.367657450087461e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Authorities proposed to relocate the young men there and offered them housing for three weeks.\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most did not want to take up the offer, saying they feared being further isolated and with no plan after the three weeks ran out.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This website and associated newspapers adhere to the Independent Press Standards Organisation's     Editors' Code of Practice.\", \"from\": 1971, \"to\": 2097, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have a complaint about the editorial content which relates to     inaccuracy or intrusion, then pleasecontact the editor here.\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are dissatisfied with the response provided you cancontact IPSO here  \\u00a9 2001-2025.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Epping Forest Guardianis owned and operated by Newsquest Media Group Ltd, an audited local newspaper network.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2330, \"end\": 2343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epping_Forest\", \"score\": 0.9999953618387978, \"rank\": 4.63818290826676e-06, \"text\": \"Epping Forest\", \"types\": [\"Q422211\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epping_Forest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Epping_Forest\"}, {\"begin\": 2377, \"end\": 2402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Newsquest Media Group Ltd\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Newsquest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/re